  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of sysmon-qt</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>sysmon-qt</application> by running the following
commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>cd src               &amp;&amp;
qmake6 sysmon-qt.pro &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>cp sysmon-qt                 /usr/bin                 &amp;&amp;
cp ../data/sysmon-qt.desktop /usr/share/applications/ &amp;&amp;
cp ../data/sysmon-qt.png     /usr/share/pixmaps/</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

